overview: "SKE Senyou Gekijou wa Aki made ni Dekiru no ka?" was SKE48's Spring Concert in 2012, held in Nippon Gaishi Hall, Nagoya.  2 different shows were done in the time span of 2 days, from April 14 - April 15, 2012. This concert was the graduation concert of SKE48 members Mano Haruka, Ono Haruka, and Yamada Erika.
tagline: Will SKE48's theatre be ready by Autumn?
title: SKE48 Spring Concert 2012
